OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F405A1774865180
OL,3,CHalf a million gather in London for
OL,4,Cbiggest anti-far right demo, say
OL,5,Corganisers
OL,7,FAn estimated half a million people
OL,8,Fgathered in London for "the biggest
OL,9,Fdemonstration ever against the far
OL,10,Fright", organisers said.
OL,12,FProtesters carrying placards saying
OL,13,F"No to racism, no to Trump", and
OL,14,F"Refugees welcome" marched through the
OL,15,Fcapital to Whitehall amid a heavy
OL,16,Fpolice presence, with officers lining
OL,17,Fthe streets.
OL,26,@pD@XOUrD@FO]uD@AOUuD@[O]vD@AOUvD@RO]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G1/17
