FL,406,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40502
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F405A1774865180
OL,3,CHalf a million gather in London for
OL,4,Cbiggest anti-far right demo, say
OL,5,Corganisers
OL,7,FOrganisers said their estimates showed
OL,8,Fthey had successfully outnumbered the
OL,9,FTommy Robinson-led Unite the Kingdom
OL,10,Frally in London in September.
OL,12,FThat demonstration ` organised by
OL,13,Fright-wing activist Robinson, whose
OL,14,Freal name is Stephen Yaxley-Lennon `
OL,15,Fwas attended by between 110,000 and
OL,16,F150,000 people, while about 5,000 were
OL,17,Finvolved in an anti-racism counter-
OL,18,Fdemonstration.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G2/17
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,406,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40503
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F405A1774865180
OL,3,CHalf a million gather in London for
OL,4,Cbiggest anti-far right demo, say
OL,5,Corganisers
OL,7,FThere were several incidents of
OL,8,Fviolent disorder which left some
OL,9,Fpolice officers injured on that
OL,10,Foccasion, and the event was condemned
OL,11,Fat the time by Prime Minister Sir Keir
OL,12,FStarmer, who said it had left people
OL,13,Ffeeling "more scared than they were
OL,14,Fbefore".
OL,16,FOn Saturday, organisers said people
OL,17,Fhad gathered for a "peaceful"
OL,18,Fdemonstration against "hatred and
OL,19,Fdivision and racism".
OL,26,@uD@IOUvD@GO]yD@TOUyD@]O]zD@WOU{D@TO]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G3/17
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,406,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40504
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F405A1774865180
OL,3,CHalf a million gather in London for
OL,4,Cbiggest anti-far right demo, say
OL,5,Corganisers
OL,7,FRally co-organiser Kevin Courtney,
OL,8,Fchairman of the coalition, told crowds
OL,9,Fgathered on Whitehall: "Our estimate
OL,10,Fis now that there are half a million
OL,11,Fpeople on this demonstration ` the
OL,12,Fbiggest demonstration ever against the
OL,13,Ffar right.
OL,15,F"And it gives us all confidence to
OL,16,Fcarry on. Thank you very much."
OL,18,FSpeakers included former Labour MP
OL,19,FDiane Abbott, who now sits as an
OL,20,Findependent in Parliament.
OL,26,@qD@XOUwD@AOUxD@_O]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G4/17
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
