CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F405A1774865180
OL,3,CHalf a million gather in London for
OL,4,Cbiggest anti-far right demo, say
OL,5,Corganisers
OL,7,FShe told a cheering crowd: "The
OL,8,Fturnout today is the largest anti-
OL,9,Fracist march that I have seen in my
OL,10,Flifetime, and you should all be proud
OL,11,Fof yourselves for coming out in such
OL,12,Fnumbers today."
OL,26,@oD@\OUtD@OO]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G5/17
