CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F405A1774865180
OL,3,CHalf a million gather in London for
OL,4,Cbiggest anti-far right demo, say
OL,5,Corganisers
OL,7,FSabby Dhalu, who is joint secretary of
OL,8,Fthe Together Alliance and co-convenor
OL,9,Fof Stand Up To Racism, said the UK is
OL,10,Fseeing an "unprecedented growth" in
OL,11,Fsupport for far-right organisations `
OL,12,Fbut that she believed the size of
OL,13,Fattendance on Saturday had
OL,14,F"intimidated the far right" away from
OL,15,Fa counter-protest.
OL,26,@rD@KOUrD@`O]vD@AOUvD@[O]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G6/17
