OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,406,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40507
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F405A1774865180
OL,3,CHalf a million gather in London for
OL,4,Cbiggest anti-far right demo, say
OL,5,Corganisers
OL,7,FSpeaking to the Press Association
OL,8,Fbefore the event, she said: "The Tommy
OL,9,FRobinson-led Unite the Kingdom
OL,10,Fdemonstration back in September 2025
OL,11,Fwas the biggest far-right mobilisation
OL,12,Fin British history.
OL,14,F"We believe that the majority of
OL,15,FBritish people stand against the
OL,16,Fhatred and division and racism that
OL,17,Fwas being encouraged at that
OL,18,Fdemonstration and by these types of
OL,19,Forganisations, and it's time to act."
OL,26,@pD@]OUvD@AOU{D@eO]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G7/17
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,406,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40508
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F405A1774865180
OL,3,CHalf a million gather in London for
OL,4,Cbiggest anti-far right demo, say
OL,5,Corganisers
OL,7,FAsked if she was concerned about
OL,8,Fpotential counter-protests and
OL,9,Fdisorder, Ms Dhalu said: "We're
OL,10,Fconfident that the size of our
OL,11,Fmobilisation here today has actually
OL,12,Fintimidated the far-right, and I think
OL,13,Fthey feel that they are not confident
OL,14,Fenough to stand against us because
OL,15,Fthey know that we're going to be out
OL,16,Fin big numbers."
OL,26,@qD@ZOUxD@PO]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G8/17
