FL,406,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40509
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F405A1774865180
OL,3,CHalf a million gather in London for
OL,4,Cbiggest anti-far right demo, say
OL,5,Corganisers
OL,7,FSinger Billy Bragg, who ahead of the
OL,8,Fmarch criticised US president Donald
OL,9,FTrump as "a constant reminder of the
OL,10,Fcruel realities of the politics of
OL,11,Fdivision", performed some protest
OL,12,Fsongs onstage at Whitehall.
OL,14,FHe said while concerns some have about
OL,15,Fmigration might be justified, "their
OL,16,Fsolutions are not justifiable in any
OL,17,Fway or sort".
OL,26,@qD@JOUsD@IO]wD@_OUyD@LO]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G9/17
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,406,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40510
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F405A1774865180
OL,3,CHalf a million gather in London for
OL,4,Cbiggest anti-far right demo, say
OL,5,Corganisers
OL,7,FHe added: "Re migration, the forced
OL,8,Fdeportation of our fellow citizens,
OL,9,Fwe've seen what that looks like in the
OL,10,FUnited States of America.
OL,12,F"And if it does come to that in this
OL,13,Fcountry then we will have to be as
OL,14,Fcourageous as the people of
OL,15,FMinneapolis who stood in the streets
OL,16,Fto deny (deportations)."
OL,26,@oD@KOUtD@AOUxD@XO]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                G10/17
