PN,40511
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F405A1774865180
OL,3,CHalf a million gather in London for
OL,4,Cbiggest anti-far right demo, say
OL,5,Corganisers
OL,7,FOrganisers estimated around 20,000
OL,8,Fpeople were gathering in Trafalgar
OL,9,FSquare for a related event where
OL,10,Fmusical performers include former
OL,11,FLittle Mix singer Leigh-Anne Pinnock.
OL,13,FAn estimated thousand people joined to
OL,14,Fmarch together specifically against
OL,15,FChristian nationalism.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                G11/17
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
