FL,406,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40512
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F405A1774865180
OL,3,CHalf a million gather in London for
OL,4,Cbiggest anti-far right demo, say
OL,5,Corganisers
OL,7,FThe Bishop of Croydon, Rosemarie
OL,8,FMallett, told a church service ahead
OL,9,Fof the demonstration that she stood
OL,10,Fwith "all people of goodwill who seek
OL,11,Fto build diverse and inclusive
OL,12,Fcommunities" and she and other
OL,13,FChristians are "committed to building
OL,14,Fbridges rather than barriers and to
OL,15,Fliving out Jesus's command to love our
OL,16,Fneighbours".
OL,18,FIn December, Robinson led another
OL,19,F"Unite The Kingdom" event in London,
OL,20,Fwith a carol concert claiming to "put
OL,21,Fthe Christ back into Christmas".
OL,26,@rD@FOUtD@LO]uD@POUxD@KO]{D@AOU{D@SO]|D@
OL,26,AbOU}D@_O]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                G12/17
