CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F405A1774865180
OL,3,CHalf a million gather in London for
OL,4,Cbiggest anti-far right demo, say
OL,5,Corganisers
OL,7,FEarlier this year, a number of Church
OL,8,Fof England bishops voiced their
OL,9,Frejection of "the use of Christian
OL,10,Fsymbols" by people trying to
OL,11,Fintimidate others, in the face of
OL,12,Fcommunity anxiety about the flying of
OL,13,FSt George's and Union flags.
OL,15,FAs Saturday's rally began, there were
OL,16,Fshouts from a group of around 10
OL,17,Fcounter protesters. One member of the
OL,18,Fgroup was carrying an Israeli flag.
OL,26,@qD@NOUrD@HO]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                G13/17
