PN,40514
SC,0014
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F405A1774865180
OL,3,CHalf a million gather in London for
OL,4,Cbiggest anti-far right demo, say
OL,5,Corganisers
OL,7,FA separate march organised by the
OL,8,FPalestine Coalition also took place
OL,9,Fand joined the route of the Together
OL,10,FAlliance before the groups formed up
OL,11,Ffor the rally on Whitehall.
OL,13,FOfficers imposed public order
OL,14,Fconditions banning the joint rally
OL,15,Ffrom continuing after 5pm.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                G14/17
