CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F405A1774865180
OL,3,CHalf a million gather in London for
OL,4,Cbiggest anti-far right demo, say
OL,5,Corganisers
OL,7,FDaniel Kebede, general secretary of
OL,8,Fthe National Education Union (NEU) `
OL,9,Fspeaking ahead of the Together demo,
OL,10,Faccused some of those in power of
OL,11,F"using racism to feather their own
OL,12,Fnests".
OL,14,FHe said the "toxic climate that is
OL,15,Ftaking place in society festers into
OL,16,Fschools", where he said there has been
OL,17,F"an increase in racist incidents,
OL,18,Fwhether that's directed towards
OL,19,Fteachers and support staff, or pupil-
OL,20,Fon-pupil, so it's incredibly difficult
OL,21,Fat the moment".
OL,26,@sD@AOUtD@FO]vD@MOUxD@HO]yD@AOU}D@NO]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                G15/17
