PN,40516
SC,0016
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F405A1774865180
OL,3,CHalf a million gather in London for
OL,4,Cbiggest anti-far right demo, say
OL,5,Corganisers
OL,7,FMet Police Deputy Assistant
OL,8,FCommissioner Jon Savell said this will
OL,9,Fbe a "busy weekend for our officers
OL,10,Fbut we have detailed plans in place to
OL,11,Fensure all groups protesting this
OL,12,Fweekend can do so lawfully and without
OL,13,Fcausing serious disruption to other
OL,14,FLondoners, businesses or visitors".
OL,16,FAs well as the mass demonstration, a
OL,17,Fnumber of protests against the Iranian
OL,18,Fregime ` both static assemblies and
OL,19,Fmarches ` were taking place in the
OL,20,FWestminster area on both Saturday and
OL,21,FSunday, the Metropolitan Police said.
OL,26,@qD@FOUvD@bO]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                G16/17
